snippet.title: Bookshop Simulator - Announce Trailer
snippet.description:
Open your own bookshop! Order books, stock your shelves, and earn revenue. Use your profits to customize and expand your store. Collect rare books that give powerful abilities. Adopt a cat to keep you and your customers company along the way!

We created this game because we love the job sim genre and we wanted one with a cozy bookstore vibe. If this interests you, add the game to your Wishlist on Steam.

Steam Page: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3467040/Bookshop_Simulator/

Website: https://www.bookshopsimulator.com/

Please leave feedback and suggestions in the comments, we want to hear from you!
